Example of application
----------------------

Growing oyster mushroom in cellar
Cooperation with MM1A and MM2A analog controllers 

Inputs:
  in1:  (unused)
  in2:  water pressure (closed: good)
  in3:  growing hyphae/mushroom (closed: hyphae)
  in4:  (unused)

Error light:
  err1: bad relative humidity
  err2: bad water pressure
  err3: (unused)
  err4: bad temperature

Outputs:
  out1: humidifying (active in 5 s)
  out2: lighting
  out3: ventilation
  out4: heating
